
Ranger Help for: armour
=======================

SUMMARY:    
Rangers are free to wear almost all armour. The only armours they have
trouble getting by in is plate or platemail armours. Mainly because it
is so clanky and noisey, kind of takes away any surprise a stealthy Ranger
might have. Chainmail armours are still somewhat noisey, but not to the
point of being restrictive.

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: weapons

